name: plus_comm
text: forall a b : nat, a + b = b + a.

name: plus_0_r
text: forall n : nat, n + 0 = n.

name: plus_0_l
text: forall n : nat, 0 + n = n.

name: mult_0_r
text: forall n : nat, n * 0 = 0.

name: mult_0_l
text: forall n : nat, 0 * n = 0.

name: mult_comm
text: forall a b : nat, a * b = b * a.

name: plus_assoc
text: forall a b c : nat, a + (b + c) = (a + b) + c.

name: mult_assoc
text: forall a b c : nat, a * (b * c) = (a * b) * c.

name: length_rev
text: forall (A : Type) (l : list A), length (rev l) = length l.

name: app_length
text: forall (A : Type) (l1 l2 : list A), length (l1 ++ l2) = length l1 + length l2.

name: rev_app_distr
text: forall (A : Type) (l1 l2 : list A), rev (l1 ++ l2) = rev l2 ++ rev l1.

name: and_comm
text: forall P Q : Prop, P /\ Q -> Q /\ P.

name: or_comm
text: forall P Q : Prop, P \/ Q -> Q \/ P.

name: plus_succ_r
text: forall n m : nat, n + S m = S (n + m).

name: mult_succ_r
text: forall n m : nat, n * S m = n + n * m.

name: le_refl
text: forall n : nat, n <= n.

name: le_trans
text: forall n m p : nat, n <= m -> m <= p -> n <= p.

name: nat_ind_principle
text: forall P : nat -> Prop, P 0 -> (forall n, P n -> P (S n)) -> forall n, P n.

name: list_ind_principle
text: forall (A : Type) (P : list A -> Prop), P [] -> (forall (a : A) (l : list A), P l -> P (a :: l)) -> forall l, P l.

name: eq_refl
text: forall (A : Type) (x : A), x = x.
